alted butter","2 tsp fine sea salt","ground black pepper, to taste"]},{"title":"Dumplings","content":["10 g fresh horseradish, sliced (1 cm)","225 g ricotta cheese, drained","200 g pasta flour, plus extra for dusting","2 egg yolks, from medium eggs","½ orange, finely grated zest only","olive oil, for greasing","500 g water, for steaming, plus extra for mixing","200 g sour cream","40 g creamed horseradish or horseradish relish","fine sea salt, to taste","ground black pepper, to taste"]}],"id":"r178679","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-PwXFVxASV6Y\/XZMyG1dlMzI\/AAAAAAAAagk\/G6BAjmVFgG4dG8DB2tf67SEtCQ8BuDJXACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_44MZjx3nLu8VSPxI.png","title":"Beetroot Soup, Horseradish Dumplings","publishedAt":"2017-10-09T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"20 g","fat":"47 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"31 g","calories":"2650 kJ \/ 638 kcal"},"usefulItems":"frying pan, soup bowls, soup tureen, hob","hintsAndTricks":["To roast raw beetroot, trim then wrap in foil and place in an oven for <nobr>45 minutes<\/nobr> (180°C). Peel while still warm."],"basicInfo":["easy","40m","1h 15m","8 portions"]}